  "markdown_content": "\n## K4 — Universal Authentication Agent — Core System Component\n\nStatus: Enabled\n\nMandate: A dedicated authentication agent must be permanently available as a core Y-OS component.\n\nResponsibilities:\n\n- Logins, OTP, CAPTCHA, password creation — for all other agents\nInternal State Table (per service):\n\n- Methods tried\n- Status\n- Credential used\nBehavior:\n\n- Selects the fastest validated method\n- Checks monthly for superior methods"
